channel.title: Need help setting up default gateway
channel.description: Ok, I download JDK, finished working on my server, set up an no-ip, and right when I saw the light at the end of the tunnel when I went to find the ipconfig it said it couldn't recognize it as an internel or external command. Any1 know how to fix this?

item.title: Need help setting up default gateway
item.dc:creator: @noobspure50 noobspure50
item.description:
@noobspure50 wrote:

thats how u can ipconfig -.-[br][br][size=1]Posted on: April 25, 2009, 05:53:38 pm[/size][hr]put this in your path in environmental variables

%SystemRoot%\system32;%SystemRoot%;%SystemRoot%\System32\Wbem;C:\Program Files\QuickTime\QTSystem\

then your classpath

CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_13\bin;%CLASSPATH%;

that will work
